data.description: Unlike anything you've ever seen.  There are so many special and unique features about this home. This is the perfect home for a large or growing family.  Tucked away on 3 private, wooded acres the entrance to the home boats a beautiful two story foyer and lovely spiral stair case.  The Dining room seats 12 and is perfect for entertaining holiday meals.  The family room and den also allow for lots of fun entertaining.  All of the upstairs bedrooms have an on-suite private or semi private bathroom giving each family member lots of privacy.  The fully finished basement apartment is perfect for a teen or mother-in-law suite or will make a perfect income property.  The one bedroom basement apartment has it's own private entrance as well as its own garage parking.  Estimated rent on the basement apartment is $900 per month.  There are very few homes like this one the market.
